Name: Fried Rice
Description: Fried rice is a dish of cooked rice that has been stir-fried in a wok ..

Name: Noodles
Description: Noodles are a type of food made from unleavened dough which is either rolled flat and cut, stretched, or extruded, into long strips or strings.

Name: Momo
Description: Momo are bite-size dumplings made with a spoonful of stuffing wrapped in dough. Momo are usually steamed, though they are sometimes fried or steam-fried.
